              exp←{⎕ML←3 ⋄ (⍵≠',')⊂⍵}¨exts[inds]
              mask[inds]←n←⍬∘⍴∘⍴¨exp
              (exts types)←mask∘/¨exts types
              exts[(n/inds)++\~∊n↑¨1]←⊃,/exp
          :EndIf
          ms.Config.ContentTypes←exts,[1.1]types
      :Else
          1 ms.Log'No content types defined?'
      :EndIf
    ∇


